    <description>&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/default/original/1X/666d4d935aa0edbba2415181ecdd6b80253f3773.png&quot; width=&quot;446&quot; height=&quot;500&quot;&gt;

We changed [The Sheriff&#39;s](http://tol.wikia.com/wiki/The_Sheriff) ability today - The former ability:

&lt;del&gt;**Day Ability 1 (Reveal Mustache):**
**[1 attempt power]** The Sheriff can make the system of the game reveal himself as The Sheriff. Other players will know that you are The Sheriff&lt;/del&gt;

is now removed. The mustache has been shaved (in spirit). _The new ability is at night:_

**Night Ability 2 (Posse Comitatus):** 
[1x] Recruit a fellow Blue Dragon to become a [Knight](http://tol.wikia.com/wiki/The_Knight) class. Cannot convert Royalty or Unique classes. Reveals the Sheriff to the target, even if unable to convert.

&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/default/original/1X/838a3ee5ef71c2db60937605b29488deadd5a81d.png&quot; width=&quot;446&quot; height=&quot;500&quot;&gt;

What do you guys think?



